{"tid":1462444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何謂癱瘓機場","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:46:48.000Z","uid":76867,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f064b3d0782760762f797ff960365efb4e3b90cf","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"其實尋日癱瘓機場既癱瘓<br />\n係指人太多塞爆左個機場而唔係主動阻撓旅客<br />\n機場係終極和理非既地方<br />\n<br />\n警察咩都做唔到都係因為太和平<br />\n換句話黎講 亂既唯一得益者係警察<br />\n如果你起我底 我今朝已經講左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察只有一個方法重奪機場主權</span></strong></span><br />\n佢地無辦法強行清場 所以只會軟攻<br />\n<br />\n政府唯一重奪機場主導既戰略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460431</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔夠人塞唔Cancel flight咪唔好癱<br />\n繼續和理飛對外講發生咩事<br />\n69到而家 好多野可以同旅客解釋"},{"pid":"ddfc82306eacda29d0a0ccf37c9ac41e87015f4a","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"瘋狂推post"},{"pid":"13ae33a6ae135f3c42824b0e97f48c0577c3242a","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"1a3d401fce5ca3766a89e2000228153717dfab85","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"3ddd59af54581d96971a9daa36eeaa26d5741d3a","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"3/20"},{"pid":"32a82a9eecc13d089f6afa7c8ddbabef8f630de0","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"4/20"},{"pid":"6558af6e934927f8ff8aff51e175c3b47d968692","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"5/20"},{"pid":"67ee16cd87faea2b44b88c63d250f8144bb9330d","tid":1462444,"uid":76867,"like":0,"disli